nodes.text: The year 33,908 before the Battle of Yavin, also known as 2,545 after the Tho Yor Arrival, was a year in galactic history. That year, a member of the Je'daii Order was recorded saying the phrase "At the heart of any poor soul not at one with the Force, there is only void." Though the Je'daii's identity was lost to history, the phrase itself endured as a common saying in the Je'daii Order.
